    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies the Real-time Transport Protocol (RTP) payload format for ITU-T Recommendation G.711.0.  ITU-T Rec.  G.711.0 defines a lossless and stateless compression for G.711 packet payloads typically used in IP networks.  This document also defines a storage mode format for G.711.0 and a media type registration for the G.711.0 RTP payload format.</t>
    </abstract>
